structure.unit: SOVEREIGNTY AND JURISDICTION OF THE COMMONWEALTH

law.text: The Fordsville (Ohio County) Tug-of-War Championship Contest is named and designated as the Kentucky State Tug-of-War Championship.
law.history: Amended 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 186, sec. 1, effective July 13, 1990. -- Created 1984 Ky. Acts ch. 76, sec. 1, effective July 13, 1984.
